## 1. The "Distribution" Mindset
Inspired by industrial distribution, Sourabh argues that the scale of your business is limited only by your distribution volume. 
* **Surface Area:** Content increases the "points of contact" a founder has with the market.
* **Efficiency:** High-level founders use tools (like Zoom or AI) to talk once and distribute everywhere.

## 2. Platform-Specific Psychology
| Platform | Primary Function | Business Goal |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **LinkedIn** | Authority & Narrative | B2B Connections / Investor PR |
| **YouTube** | Trust & Depth | Detailed Tutorials / High-Ticket Sales |
| **Instagram** | Connection & Personality | Consumer Trust / Brand Vibe |

## 3. Beyond Social Media Management
Sourabh redefines "Content Marketing" as an all-encompassing service:
* **Internal Content:** Training materials and culture docs.
* **External Content:** Social posts and video series.
* **Live Infrastructure:** Crafting the PPTs and talk tracks for founder sessions to ensure the narrative is consistent across all touchpoints.

